author: Disney
description:
D23 Gold Members are invited to uncover archival treasures and celebrate Disney’s rich past and present—and even glimpse the future—in the virtual D23 Gold Theater presented by State Farm with “Walt Disney Archives 55th Anniversary Celebration!”  
  
Enjoy the presentations at the “D23 Spotlight Series: Walt Disney Archives 55th Anniversary Celebration” event in Glendale, California on June 1, 2025. D23 Gold Members will hear from archivists, Disney Legends, and luminaries about how the Archives collects, preserves, and shares the thousands of treasures in its collection. 
  
We invite you to join us for this special installment of our monthly virtual event series in the D23 Gold Theater. Available to watch at https://theater.d23.com/ Thursday, July 31, 2025, at 6 p.m. PT / 9 p.m. ET. With an encore presentation on Saturday, August 2, 2025, at 11 a.m. PT / 2 p.m. ET.   
  
Not a D23 Gold Member? Become one today https://d23.com/join/ and let the magic begin!
